        </a>
        <a class="doc-card" href="/docs/selection-action" hx-get="/docs/selection-action" hx-target="#content" hx-push-url="true">
            <strong>Selection and action</strong>
            <span>Use request intent to choose a child partial or let Go decide the next render.</span>
